  "prompt": "Which are the best 3 and 4 star hotels in Goa?",
  "response": "Goa, a popular tourist destination in India, offers numerous options for accommodations, ranging from budget hotels to luxury resorts. Here are some highly recommended 3 and 4-star hotels in Goa:\n\n### Three-Star Hotels\n1. **La Sunila Suites**\n   - Location: Baga\n   **Features:**\n   - Proximity to Baga Beach.\n   - Spacious suites with kitchenettes.\n   - Swimming pool and an in-house restaurant.\n\n2. **De Alturas Resort**\n   - Location: Candolim\n   **Features:**\n   - Comfortable rooms with modern amenities.\n   - Pool area and spa.\n   - Close to Candolim Beach.\n\n3. **Treehouse Blue**\n   - Location: Majorda\n   **Features:**\n   - Apartment-style accommodations.\n   - Serene environment away from the hustle.\n   - Pool facility and thoughtful service.\n\n### Four-Star Hotels\n1. **The Grand Inn**\n   - Location: Calangute\n   **Features:**\n   - Elegant rooms and modern facilities.\n   - Short distance to Calangute Beach.\n   - Swimming pool and multiple dining options.\n\n2. **Kyriad Hotel Goa**\n   - Location: Candolim\n   **Features:**\n   - Stylish rooms and suites.\n   - Extensive buffet breakfast.\n   - Close to the beach with outdoor pool.\n\n3. **Hard Rock Hotel Goa**\n   - Location: Calangute\n   **Features:**\n   - Music-themed design and luxury amenities.\n   - Various entertainment options.\n   - Excellent dining and poolside bar.\n\n4. **Azzure By Spree**\n   - Location: Calangute\n   **Features:**\n   - Chic style and well-equipped rooms.\n   - Great hospitality and service.\n   - Rooftop pool and easy beach access.\n\nThese hotels are known for their good service, comfortable accommodations, and convenient locations near various attractions in Goa. When choosing a hotel, consider factors like proximity to beaches, local attractions, amenities offered, and guest reviews to find the best fit for your visit.",
